TITLE: Registering and Enabling Custom Fixers in PHP CS Fixer Configuration
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet demonstrates how to register custom fixers and enable them in the PHP CS Fixer configuration file. It shows the structure for creating a new PhpCsFixer\Config object, registering custom fixers, and setting rules to enable them.
