TITLE: Adding custom rules to PSR12 ruleset
DESCRIPTION: Configuration that extends the PSR12 ruleset with additional custom rules. This example adds strict parameter type checking and requires short array syntax.
SOURCE: https://github.com/php-cs-fixer/php-cs-fixer/blob/master/doc/config.rst#2025-04-23_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
<?php

$finder = (new PhpCsFixer\Finder())
    ->in(__DIR__)
;

return (new PhpCsFixer\Config())
    ->setRules([
        '@PSR12' => true,
        'strict_param' => true,
        'array_syntax' => ['syntax' => 'short'],
    ])
    ->setFinder($finder)
;
```

