TITLE: Fixing Non-Monolithic Code with Inline HTML in PHP
DESCRIPTION: This example shows the rule's behavior when configured with 'fix_non_monolithic_code' set to true, which allows it to fix code with inline HTML.
SOURCE: https://github.com/php-cs-fixer/php-cs-fixer/blob/master/doc/rules/control_structure/no_alternative_syntax.rst#2025-04-23_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: diff
CODE:
```
--- Original
+++ New
-<?php if ($condition): ?>
+<?php if ($condition) { ?>
 Lorem ipsum.
-<?php endif; ?>
+<?php } ?>
```

