TITLE: Converting Short Array Syntax to Long Array Syntax in PHP (Custom Configuration)
DESCRIPTION: This example shows how to configure the rule to use the long array syntax, converting modern short array syntax back to the traditional array() notation with the 'syntax' => 'long' configuration.
